name: idwallSDK
summary: Mobile SDK to support liveness-proof and document detection integrating with idwall services

license.text: Copyright 2020 idwall, ltda. All rights reserved.

description:
Our iOS SDK provides the following services: capture quality-scanned documents, capture selfie with liveness 
proof and send information to our server, where all functionality returns real-time feedback to the user, 
thus the user will always have a response when using our SDK.
